【Easy Assembly & After-sale Service】The AODK office desk come with detailed instructions, all parts are clearly labeled, what you need to do is following instructions step-by-step. If your AODK computer desk arrives damaged, missing part or scratched, please feel free to contact us, our professional customer support team will help you solve the problem within 24 hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very practical and looks nice too
reviews.reviewText: The storage drawers are a wonderful part of this desk. They are cloth, but they have a fake wood front that helps to stabilize them. The desk is sturdy, lights are nice, and has plenty of room for everything. My computer is too large to fit on the intended shelf, so any medium to large PC tower is not going to fit there. Overall a very nice desk for the money.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great. Sturdy. Lots of shelf space.
reviews.reviewText: Desk took over an hour to assemble. There are many pieces. At the end of assembly 3 of the 6 specific screws needed to assemble the monitor stand were not included. I will be contacting the seller. They included a contact info. sheet in the box. I set this up in the ‘left’ configuration and had zero issues with holes missing like that one star review had mentioned happened with their desk.Other areas to note:- I have a 34” ultra wide monitor and it fits nicely on the monitor stand.- The cloth drawers are better in terms of strength then I expected them to be.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great desk, long assembly
reviews.reviewText: It’s a great desk and good for the value. Assembling it took the better part of a night after work, be prepared for it to be your evening. The desk is sturdy but does creak a little if I shake it a bit. The depth is enough to be comfortable, and the side of the L-shape is enough for me to keep a second laptop on.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Product looks good, sturdy, and well made
reviews.reviewText: I was reallly excited when I got this delivered so fast. Thank you! Fast shipping is always the first way to win me over. So as I am putting it together I begin to realize that not just with this product but most desks there are a lot of screws. I do not mean just a lot I mean a lot of different screws. I really hate that part but hey thats a personal preference not a flaw in the product itself. The warnings tell you to not to use the wrong screw as it might damage the desk. True. Didnt happen to me since I can follow instructions. However I will say this Do not try and over tighten the screws because they keep going and if you are not paying attention it will go through to the other side. I almost had this happen but was paying attention and listening for when I thought far enough was far enough. I say this because some places the product will not sit flush which would make you want to keep tightening the screw, but just do not do it! Thanks. Thats all I have to say for this product. All in all good product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and well worth the money.
reviews.reviewText: First off, super easy to assemble. Probably took me longer to unpack from the box than actually put together. Instructions were clear and offered both the left hand and right hand assembly instructions. Once together, it’s super sturdy. No shake or wobble. I could stand on it and jump and still feel safe. Now my spouse wants one for their home office space.

reviews.reviewText: Nice desk I love it but I emailed about three weeks after I received it due to the strip coming off the front of the desk to see if they can fix it and no response back

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Garbage, Unfinished Product
reviews.reviewText: DO NOT BUY THIS PRODUCT!!!! This is the worst, low quality piece of garbage I have ever bought on Amazon.I bought this desk as a birthday present for myself since I needed a new desk. I'm pretty good at assembling furniture and haven't had any issues with this sort of thing in the past. When I started assembling the desk, I went with the left version instructions. When I got to the step where I was supposed to attach the "D" labeled wood pieces, I noticed that there were only 2 holes drilled into each piece, totaling at 4 holes not drilled. There was allegedly supposed to be 4 holes on each piece of wood. I know people aren't good at reading furniture assembly instructions, but I took a lot of machine shop classes and know what I'm doing.Whatever invalids at the factory didn't drill all the necessary holes into the product. I was was robbed of $30 because I had to buy the necessary drill bits to fix this issue. I ended up missing raid because I didn't have a desk to play games on. I was up until 12am making the desk that should've been done by 8pm. DO NOT BUY THIS PRODUCT! YOU ARE WASTING YOUR MONEY!
